<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>{{bot_name}} - I'm your 'not milk' supplier!</title>
        <link rel="favicon icon" href="../static/milk.png">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/style.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="wrapper">
                <div class="navbar">
                    <div class="section brand">
                        <a href="/"><img src="../static/milk.png"> NOT MILK</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section links">
                        <a href="/leaderboard" class="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple" id="leader-icon"></i> Leaderboard</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section searchbox">
                        <form action="/search" method="get">
                            <label for="query"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></label>
                            <input type="text" name="query" placeholder="Find user...">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="page-content" style="justify-content:center;">
                    <!-- visit card -->
                    {{#if bot_name}}
                    {{#if bot_icon}}
                    {{#if bot_maintainer}}
                    <div class="block brand">
                        <div class="block-info brand">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <img src="{{bot_icon}}">
                            </div>
                            <div class="summary">
                                <p>
                                    <a href="https://twitch.tv/{{bot_name}}">@{{bot_name}}</a> is a game bot
                                    that supplies 'not milk' to your chat! Maintained by <a href="https://twitch.tv/{{bot_maintainer}}">@{{bot_maintainer}}</a>.
                                </p>
                                <p>type <span class="command inline" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">ðŸ¥› join</span> into any chat room that has @{{bot_name}} if you want this bot. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{/if}}
                    {{/if}}

                    <!-- features block -->
                    <div class="block features">
                        <h1 class="block-title">Features</h1>

                        <div class="block-list">
                            <div class="block-info">
                                <div class="summary">
                                    <h2>'Not milk' game!</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        Collect 'not milk' glasses!
                                        You can collect a random number of glasses of 'not milk' or you can steal from a random person.
                                        But be careful, you might get stolen from you too!
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        To test yourself in 'not milk' game, use this command:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› sip
                                        </div>

                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        Or if you want to pump 'not milk' out of someome, use these commands:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› suck USERNAME
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        Or maybe you want to give your 'not milk' to someone:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› give AMOUNT to USERNAME
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        If you want to try your luck, you can try roulette:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› roulette NUMBER or PERCENT or all
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="icon">
                                    <img src="https://cdn.7tv.app/emote/62073757591acf4392f570bc/4x.webp">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="block-info">
                                <div class="summary">
                                    <h2 class="title">Scoring and leaderboards</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        Know the best 'not milk' sippers with the command:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› top
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        Do you want to know what position you are in? Use the command:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› place
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="icon">
                                    <img src="https://cdn.7tv.app/emote/61ad779c15b3ff4a5bb9a785/4x.webp">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="block-info">
                                <div class="summary">
                                    <h2>'Non-Fungible Milks'</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        'Non-Fungible Milk' or NFM is the new fun for milk consumers!
                                        With your milk, you can create your own unique NFM and show off to your friends
                                        about how unique it is and that only you have it and it will be true!
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        To create your NFM, use this command:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› nfm
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        You can sell your NFM 24 hours after purchase.
                                        Keep in mind that the 'milk rate' is used in pricing, which is now <b>{{rate}}</b>.
                                        To sell, use the command:
                                        <div class="command" onclick="copy(this.innerHTML.trim());">
                                            ðŸ¥› sellnfm ID
                                        </div>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="icon">
                                    <img src="https://cdn.7tv.app/emote/6345aa2c05c2b2cd864d73c9/4x.webp">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="block-info">
                                <div class="summary">
                                    <h2 class="title">soonâ„¢...</h2>
                                    <p>
                                        The bot is at a very early stage of development, so there is very little function so far.
                                        You can follow <a href="https://github.com/ilotterytea/not-milk">the development of the bot on GitHub.</a>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="icon">
                                    <img src="https://cdn.7tv.app/emote/62313510b1ac2f158885fb66/4x.webp">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        function copy(text) {
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
            alert('Successfully copied to your clipboard');
        }
    </script>
</html>
